{"tid":525018,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【男士小心】變態男更衣室偷拍「波牛」 手機藏40條裸男短片斷正","createTime":"2018-01-10T08:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T08:29:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a1b077ea39d4f2209a6314a844db353ab9dfe3","tid":525018,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180110/large/1515567219_ff35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180110%2Flarge%2F1515567219_ff35.jpg&h=99a5397e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n觀塘遊樂場出現偷拍狂！下午1時許，一批男子在遊樂場的足球場內踢波後，到更衣室更衣洗澡及閒談，其間一名變態男子用手機偷拍各人沐浴情況，被更衣室內一名剛沐浴的市民發現，當場揭發其變態行為，遭近十人合力制服，並發現其手機內有多段近月疑在更衣室內偷拍的裸男片段。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者稱，偷拍男被制服後，還強裝鎮定，聲稱只是路過上址如廁及洗手，否認刻意偷拍。但警員接報到場拘捕涉案男子後，卻在其手機內發現超過40條偷拍短片，至少2段是今日拍的，亦有上月拍攝的，相信他是慣犯，部分影片更拍到受害男性的裸體全相，於是把他拘捕帶署調查。現場消息稱，被捕人有刑事案底，曾短暫入獄，近月才出獄，卻不時流連上址的更衣室疑為偷拍，其所作所為已曾被其他波友嚴斥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180110/large/1515567233_9363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180110%2Flarge%2F1515567233_9363.jpg&h=7a17b3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180110/large/1515567578_bfe7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180110%2Flarge%2F1515567578_bfe7.jpg&h=d444e854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180110/large/1515567279_5170.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180110%2Flarge%2F1515567279_5170.jpg&h=ceff0bb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180110/57689496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F57689496&d=0F%2F3G%2BKy%2F4cf3VPMUpUJ2aMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=cbf15c6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180110%2F57689496&h=be14951c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180110/57689496</a>"},{"pid":"5781266587145921fed7d0788d752b8c2fff00bd","tid":525018,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:04:54.000Z","msg":"嗰啲男人都可以#metoo?"},{"pid":"3165977b45bdb6d99ddc4220aaae944346f635ef","tid":525018,"uid":122239,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ece413e04937cbaa45d7ce7a1b7cc240c4e10e","tid":525018,"uid":153566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}